# Business Requirements & Monetization Strategy

## Subscription Tiers
### Lite Plan ($4.99/month)
- 4 quotes per month with images and voice
- Basic psychological profiling
- Standard content delivery

### Standard Plan ($9.99/month)
- 12 quotes per month
- Enhanced psychological profiling
- Priority content delivery
- Basic analytics

### Premium Plan ($19.99/month)
- Daily quotes
- Commercial voice licensing
- Advanced analytics
- Priority support
- Exclusive content

### Enterprise Plan (Custom pricing)
- API access
- Commercial image licensing
- Custom integrations
- Dedicated support
- White-label options

## Revenue Streams
- **Primary**: Subscription revenue
- **Secondary**: Commercial licensing fees
- **Tertiary**: Enterprise API services
- **Future**: NFT marketplace, merchandise

## Cost Management
- **AI Generation**: Optimize with batch processing and caching
- **Infrastructure**: Use serverless and spot instances
- **Content**: Leverage public domain sources
- **Marketing**: Focus on organic growth and community building

## Market Positioning
- **Target Market**: Global mindfulness and self-improvement market
- **Competitive Advantage**: Unique AI-generated characters with Japanese wisdom
- **Differentiation**: Cultural authenticity and personalization
- **Value Proposition**: Deep, meaningful content experiences

## Success Metrics
- **User Acquisition**: MAU growth targets
- **Retention**: Monthly and annual retention rates
- **Revenue**: ARPU and LTV optimization
- **Quality**: User satisfaction and content engagement
- **Efficiency**: Cost per user and operational efficiency

## Risk Management
- **Technical**: AI generation cost control and quality assurance
- **Legal**: Copyright compliance and licensing management
- **Market**: Competition and market saturation risks
- **Operational**: Scalability and performance challenges
